{"url": "ew.com/movies/2017/07/16/martin-landau-dead-celebrities-tribute/", "text": "Martin Landau, perhaps most known for his Oscar-winning performance as Bela Lugosi in 1994\u2019s Ed Wood, died Saturday at age 89. Celebrities influenced by Landau\u2019s many decades of work \u2014 his first notable role was in Alfred Hitchcock\u2019s 1959 film North by Northwest and he has been acting ever since \u2014 reacted to the news, remembering his talent and kindness.\n\n\u201cI had the honor & joy of working/playing with Marty Landau. What a wonderful actor, what a wonderful soul,\u201d Jeff Bridges wrote on Twitter. \u201cHe loved acting so much, and that love, that excitement was contagious. Thank you, Marty, for all you gave us.\u201d\n\n\u201cWorking with Martin Landau on Ed Wood was a joy,\u201d Patricia Arquette tweeted. \u201cWhat a talented, sweet generous actor. #RealDeal.\u201d\n\nOrlando Jones posted a portrait Landau drew for him. \u201cHe took me under wing,\u201d Jones wrote. \u201cHe touched my heart. I swore to pay it forward.\u201d\n\nSee those tweets and more paying tribute to Landau below.", "images": ["https://ew.com/thmb/liYSVrlpMyBtr-AGceY4MeT92hY=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/warfare-A24-121524-8b5c02be0ac54c0284ba6ee0a2dff7db.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/S4WE5oJMuwBEtYfHDEXTeryLZsU=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/gettyimages-530891342-2000-247bb0558dea4e59a798629bbb10d630.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/yUmn28QRS_oC8m3pBidTjwqJfXY=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/gettyimages-152172530-2000-14bc060f58ec48b0ba148cde804d6a5e.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/L-dm2ivoJIpIOnPXfspcla1scEs=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Billy-Crystal-Martin-Scorsese-121524-5815e734ccae470b86b5d876e7bf9c3c.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/ILH0w_9eA-VdQz75NuaIeUby3mQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Nightbitch-120424-eb62c652a0f045e8a88dc3abf1564a43.jpg", 